modelVersions.name: v1
modelVersions.description:
16 vectors, trained on ~200 images for 5000 steps.

LR: 0.005:1000, 0.001:2000, 0.0002

Struggles with proper fairy wings, but otherwise very reliable on NAI-based models even without large prompts.
